strings: <voice_0x0100165C>Did you succeed in collecting all the games?
<voice_0x0100165D>Found what I was looking for and came back late in the evening.
<voice_0x0100165E>You cannot hide the truth from me. You can only see the light in your eyes.
<voice_0x0100165F>I want to tell you everything I have...
<voice_0x01001660>but I can't
<voice_0x01001661>Up to 1 luggage per person is planned. Accessories can be stowed in the pocket.
<voice_0x01001662>It gives you one last hope to survive in this world.
<voice_0x01001663>You found the last hope in this world. I want to give you...
<voice_0x01001664><se_high>Accuracy: Go now!
<voice_0x01001665><se_low>King of tricks: This is the room of Trodan! Thank you for your interest in this area! Totally fake! Do not touch me!
<voice_0x01001666>No need to worry, Rafson's spirit is no longer in the hall.
<voice_0x01001667>There are now seven souls among the saints.
<voice_0x01001668>The truth behind this estate has long been hidden.
<voice_0x01001669>Originally made by the Seven Sages under my leadership.
<voice_0x0100166A>they called him
<voice_0x0100166B>It is called a bud.
<voice_0x0100166C>You will need it to destroy the dark shields around Lapthorn.
<voice_0x0100166D>It becomes brittle only when broken. This is all you can do.
<voice_0x0100166E>i'll take you to his house
<voice_0x0100166F>The Dark Lord will fight you to the death...
<voice_0x01001670>However, his attack had to be countered by his team's strength.
<voice_0x01001671>Praying for strength, the four of us, one by one, called upon the spirits of our ancestors to release the power of the heavens.
<voice_0x01001672>I can't give any other advice. Do you know what to do when you meet the lord of darkness?
<voice_0x01001673>I'll explain it again.
<voice_0x01001674>For this reason, this battle can no longer be postponed. are you ready
<voice_0x01001675>just give me a moment
<voice_0x01001676>Now you must fight him. Better to use a stick.
